		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/贪食匿叶龙山王.assets/Image_28.png')" x="576" y="598" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="1004" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">山王周期性地在地上散落1或3枚火榴果，数秒后将其吞下。使用火元素可以点燃火榴果，每颗火榴果对玩家造成<span color="#ff9999">30%</span><span>伤害，对山王造成</span><span color="#ff9999">5%生命值</span><span>的真伤，若山王吞下被点燃的火榴果，则在反噬的同时使其瘫坐在地上6s。<br/>若被匿叶龙或基尼奇发射的火榴果命中山王时，除了火榴果基础的伤害外，也会对山王造成</span><span color="#ff9999">5%生命值</span><span>的真伤。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">山王吐出火榴果，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害并留下</span><span color="#ff9999">6%</span><span>伤害的燃烬；山王吞下全部3火榴果后，将吐出2枚火弹和一次热力喷发，喷发造成</span><span color="#ff9999">250%</span><span>伤害并留下燃烬。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
